headline: What’s new on Max, Netflix and other streamers in December — and which subscriptions to keep and which to pause
summary: ‘Squid Game’ is back, plus ‘Star Wars: Skeleton Crew’ and a ‘Dexter’ prequel highlight a slow month. Plus, here are the best series of the year, and recommendations for best escapist shows.
